sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant B as Browser/App
  participant D as DNS
  participant S as Server

  U->>B: Enter URL / Click link
  B->>D: Resolve domain to IP
  D-->>B: IP address
  B->>S: HTTP request (to IP)
  S-->>B: HTTP response (HTML/JSON/etc.)
  B-->>U: Render / show result

